{"id":295576,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/【图说天朝】网易看客-高考集中营/","date":"2013-05-28T03:23:26Z","modified":"2015-11-24T02:19:24Z","title":"【图说天朝】网易看客 | 高考“集中营”","content":"<p>因为一段“高考誓师大会”，河北衡水二中走红。在校外，人们讨论这里是名校加工厂，应试训练所，还是魔鬼集中营。而在校内，考生和老师宣誓要“拼尽最后一滴血”。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-295576 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vut6jmt3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUT6JMT3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUT6JMT3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUT6JMT3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vuhr5063r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUHR5063R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295609\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUHR5063R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUHR5063R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295609'>\n\t\t\t\t河北衡水二中，因为一段名为《衡水二中2013高考百日誓师》而走红。该校在临近高考100天时全校集中在操场宣誓，场面震撼，引发热议。宣誓中，领讲人带着全校学生喊“一三高考，谁与争锋。英雄少年，唯我二中”、“决战百天，我必成功！我必成功！我必成功！我必成功！”图为2013年2月26日，学生们参加高考百日誓师大会。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtjbn3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTJBN3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295599\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTJBN3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTJBN3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295599'>\n\t\t\t\t这样的誓师大会每年都会举行，而类似于誓师的各种励志行动在这里都相当常见。图为2012年5月1日，衡水二中操场上，一名学生举着写有“虎狼团”字样的旗帜参加跑操。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtdmc3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTDMC3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295592\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTDMC3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTDMC3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295592'>\n\t\t\t\t衡水市位于河北省东南部，这里以教育发达著称，曾有“北衡水、南黄冈”的说法。这里的重点中学衡水中学也创造了“衡水模式”从而闻名全国。但近年来衡水二中后来居上，无论从升学率还是宣传实力，都有大幅度提升。图为2009年6月2日，衡水二中的教室内，黑板上写着“拼尽最后一滴血，奋战到底我坚持”。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt5j93r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT5J93R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295582\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT5J93R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT5J93R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295582'>\n\t\t\t\t打开衡水二中的官方网站，该校称“扛鼎2012高考”，而对手衡水中学则称“高考成绩13连冠，再创河北新奇迹”。相对于“衡水模式”，衡水二中也提出了自己的办学思路——“原生态教育”，声称关注和尊重生命个体、以人为本。图为2013年4月6日，外地教育观察团到衡水二中观察学习。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtfrt3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTFRT3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295594\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTFRT3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTFRT3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295594'>\n\t\t\t\t但作为一个高考考生密集的省份，完全满足“原生态”的要求也并不是一件容易的事情。在外人看来，这里的模式是不折不扣的“军事化管理”。学生们有统一的制服、遵守严格的纪律，跑操、誓师司空见惯。图为2009年6月2日，二中学校操场上，学生们在集体跑操。跑操模式也被不少外地学校仿照。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtan83r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTAN83R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295588\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTAN83R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTAN83R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295588'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2012年4月15日，二中的操场上，学生们集体参加18岁的成人礼。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtn053r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTN053R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295604\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTN053R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTN053R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295604'>\n\t\t\t\t在衡水二中，红色是整个学校的主基调，横幅、标语布满每一寸空间。有的透露着些许温暖，有些则给学生施以巨大的压力。“为了父母”、“相约清华”都可能出现在横幅中。图为2013年5月24日，学生们坐在布满标语的教学楼中。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtme33r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTME33R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295603\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTME33R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTME33R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295603'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月24日，学生们在教学楼中学习，身后则是一首名为《攀登》的诗歌。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtipk3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTIPK3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295598\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTIPK3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTIPK3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295598'>\n\t\t\t\t“王者”、“英雄”、“勇士”、“高昂着头”、“虎狼之师”则成为这里最常用的一些词语。无论是学生还是老师，都沉浸于这种狂热的气氛中。图为2012年6月2日，学生在老师带领下在教学楼内宣誓迎高考。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt9163r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9163R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9163R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9163R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295587'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月24日，衡水二中高三学生经过短暂的休息返校，这次返校后他们下一次休息将是高考结束。归校时，他们被誉为“勇士”，所有高三班主任则站在门口两侧迎接学生归来。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtc6d3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTC6D3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295590\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTC6D3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTC6D3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295590'>\n\t\t\t\t而在教室内外的每个地方，都会有一些标识或施以压力，或友好提示。让人马上便能明白身处何地。图为2009年6月1日，学校的一块黑板上写着“地毯式轰炸”、“精确制导”等字眼。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt7jd3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT7JD3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295583\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT7JD3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT7JD3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295583'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月10日，学校走廊的墙上贴着标语鼓励学生。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt71j3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT71J3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295586\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT71J3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT71J3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295586'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月1日，行人在学校里拍照。草丛里树立的牌子上是学校往届考上北大学生的简历。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtk263r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTK263R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTK263R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTK263R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295600'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月10日，学校走廊上贴着的“成绩曲线”，将每个学生历次考试成绩以曲线的方式展现。而这样类似的成绩表、成绩单布满了走廊的每一面墙。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtt3e3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTT3E3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295608\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTT3E3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTT3E3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295608'>\n\t\t\t\t在校方的压力之下，学生们自己也开始以不同方式给自己、给同学打鸡血、互相励志。图为学校的“门文化”。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugte5p3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTE5P3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295593\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTE5P3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTE5P3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295593'>\n\t\t\t\t学生们也会立下不同的目标和誓言，并以文本方式展现，督促自己完成目标。图为2009年6月2日，黑板上贴着学生们梦想的学校。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtcnm3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTCNM3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295591\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTCNM3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTCNM3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295591'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2009年6月1日，墙上贴着学生们在冲刺百日时写下的誓言，每个人的目标不同，但都会尽量具体到一个学校甚至增加多少分数，也都会留下一个“宣言”激励自己。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtha63r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHA63R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295596\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHA63R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHA63R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295596'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2009年6月2日，教室椅子上放置了各种常用的药品。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtb873r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTB873R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295589\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTB873R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTB873R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295589'>\n\t\t\t\t在这种压力之下，学校也开始想方设法为学生们增加信心，有时候也会倡导“快乐高考”。图为2012年5月30日，老师们带领学生参加拓展训练以疏解压力。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugthsb3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHSB3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295597\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHSB3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTHSB3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295597'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2011年5月29日，学生们手拉手互相鼓劲。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtgcj3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTGCJ3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295595\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTGCJ3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTGCJ3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295595'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2009年6月2日，学校发的备考提示。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtode3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTODE3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295606\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTODE3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTODE3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295606'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2012年6月5日，老师与学生拥抱，鼓励他们放松迎接即将到来的高考。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt4l73r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT4L73R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295580\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT4L73R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT4L73R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295580'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2012年6月6日，学生们抱着学校发的西瓜，临近高考，这种免费福利不少。而高考前一天晚上的晚自习，老师则会带着学生们举行一场“西瓜宴”。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt3e13r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3E13R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295578\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3E13R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3E13R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295578'>\n\t\t\t\t学校的另一项解压措施是发放“回头钱”，向每名学生发两张五元纸币，寓意“五谷丰登”、“十全十美”。图为2012年6月3日，一位老师拿着一沓新纸币准备发给学生。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtlfm3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTLFM3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295602\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTLFM3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTLFM3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295602'>\n\t\t\t\t“回头钱”也是该校的一项传统，起初为十元纸币，后为取“五谷丰登”的含义改为两张五元纸币。“回头钱”又被称之为“钱移默化”。图为2011年6月3日，学校为学生们准备的“回头钱”。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtnvd3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTNVD3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295605\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTNVD3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTNVD3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295605'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2011年6月3日，学生们举着“回头钱”朝老师挥手。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtkvm3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTKVM3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295601\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTKVM3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTKVM3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295601'>\n\t\t\t\t另外一些举措则显得温暖很多。在高考前，老师会给每个学生的手腕上戴上一副腕带、丝带或手链，还会在胸前卡上一枚胸章以示鼓励。图为2010年6月8日，学生们等待参加高考。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt05r3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT05R3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295581\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT05R3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT05R3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295581'>\n\t\t\t\t吃“幸运蛋”、过“成功门”也是学校每到高考前夕都会准备的活动。图为2009年6月7日，学生们拿着画着笑脸的鸡蛋。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt1tp3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT1TP3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295577\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT1TP3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT1TP3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295577'>\n\t\t\t\t很难说在这种狂热的气氛下，学生们是不是真的能静下心来。与狂热气氛相对的，是“冷”、“静”这样的词汇的常见，不少教室也贴着“冷静”的提示。图为2012年6月2日，学生们准备高考。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt3tk3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3TK3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295579\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3TK3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT3TK3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295579'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2012年12月30日，学校举办了元旦晚会，晚会上学生们难得表现出奔放的一面，各自展示才艺。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt9pc3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9PC3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295585\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9PC3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT9PC3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295585'>\n\t\t\t\t图为2013年5月24日，学生们在上晚自习，教室的标语上写着“为了父母”、“争分夺秒”等字样。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugtqk23r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTQK23R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295607\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTQK23R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGTQK23R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295607'>\n\t\t\t\t高考进行前，学校还会带领学生进行最后一轮鼓劲，老师们穿着红色T恤，背后写着“和你在一起”，学生们则集体穿着白色T恤，在老师的带领下喊口号。图为2011年6月8日，学生们即将参加高考。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e7%bd%91%e6%98%93%e7%9c%8b%e5%ae%a2-%e9%ab%98%e8%80%83%e9%9b%86%e4%b8%ad%e8%90%a5/8vugt8jp3r710001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT8JP3R710001-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-295584\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT8JP3R710001-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/05/8VUGT8JP3R710001-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-295584'>\n\t\t\t\t2013年5月14日，几名学生在教室里自习。对他们来说，即将到来的高考是走出高考这所“集中营”最好的方法。\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl>\n\t\t\t<br style='clear: both' />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627,13770],"tags":[10216,9364,29378,10860]}